{"tid":874281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陷家剷人唔似人鬼唔似鬼!【12歲化妝師】小男孩人氣同吸金力俱高 賺到錢買豪宅送父母","createTime":"2018-10-24T05:38:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T06:01:34.000Z","uid":65346,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1890a9f749f5cbf27450541c33e7939ef859ba4c","tid":874281,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T05:38:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181024/58825355\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181024%2F58825355&d=PLqY17On9GjrtTpqPr5A8f1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=d2061834\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181024%2F58825355&h=596ad393\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181024/58825355</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n泰國一位小化妝師經常在社交網分享自己「女人味」十足的妝容，但其實真身是一個男孩！年紀輕輕的他憑藉高超技巧人氣急升，獲邀出席各大活動，吸金力極高。他把賺到的錢為父母買了一幢豪宅，未來相信前途無可限量。<br />\n來自泰國攀牙府的納絲蒂（Nesty）小小年紀已經練得一手超強化妝技巧，他有時會畫上淡紫色眼影，配上誇張的超長眼睫毛，再戴上啡色捲曲長假髮示人，完全看不出他是男兒身。<br />\n他透過化妝教學吸引不少網民注意，更引起各大傳媒關注，早前甚至獲邀到中國行紅地毯。孝順的納絲蒂最近憑藉自己的能力，為父母建造了一棟新房子，更在社交網上載新屋照，感謝各界的支持。<br />\n他在相中寫道：「納絲蒂，是個只有12歲的孩子，卻能為父母建造新房。她得感謝每一位支持她的粉絲讓她擁有這一天，感謝每一位善良的長輩邀請她去參加各種活動。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181024/large/1540345004_dff0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181024%2Flarge%2F1540345004_dff0.jpg&h=ae2acef5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5dc4583124c039802af9ef29de6a92bf9f066eee","tid":874281,"uid":161190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T05:44:47.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"e7172ae28e72eba0b708c1d4ad77ce02003ad9bb","tid":874281,"uid":18418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5dc4583124c039802af9ef29de6a92bf9f066eee","tid":874281,"uid":161190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T05:44:47.000Z","msg":"屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T05:45:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"696c9d69cb2d6a7dc96dc85625901c855ac9ea5f","tid":874281,"uid":41317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T05:48:32.000Z","msg":"善良的長輩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42545a8db93c73450133b3026dbb0c95925ab5f5","tid":874281,"uid":65346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T05:49:11.000Z","msg":"大左又係比當地黑警玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"534687f2e6d705911342a9f465c1d25cbf00cc91","tid":874281,"uid":1870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T05:55:32.000Z","msg":"化妝技巧？是但搵個港女都贏佢啦"},{"pid":"2a175f207f4c10c87f90626c9247189586dbb8da","tid":874281,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T05:57:59.000Z","msg":"d  泰國哩最 like 炒作...自大"},{"pid":"d5efa295279a7f1cd63a3b27bab03627170cac62","tid":874281,"uid":55941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T06:00:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6feb14ef47725dd2036de4374f0c0fb7d10f4f0c","tid":874281,"uid":26329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T06:01:34.000Z","msg":"男的也好"}]}